title: Oklahoma GOP elects new chairperson
text:
Oklahoma GOP elects new chairperson UPDATED 5:16 PM CDT Oct 11, 2015 
Pam Pollard will begin as the Oklahoma GOP Chairperson effective immediately. 
Pollard was elected to fill the position after former chairman Randy Brogdon resigned the position.
